物理上的性刺激以刺激性器官或其他[[性感帶|性感帶]]為主。涉及到對性器官進行物理刺激的行為有[[自慰|自慰]]、[[感官按摩|感官按摩]]、性交、[[手交|手交]]、[[指交|指交]]。該些身體部分的敏感神經受到刺激時，受刺激者一般便會感到性興奮<ref>Schober, Justine M., and Donald Pfaff. "[https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Justine_Schober/publication/5968480_The_neurophysiology_of_sexual_arousal/links/545cf0c90cf2c1a63bfa5af6.pdf The neurophysiology of sexual arousal.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Justine_Schober/publication/5968480_The_neurophysiology_of_sexual_arousal/links/545cf0c90cf2c1a63bfa5af6.pdf |date=20170915160257 }}" Best practice & research Clinical endocrinology & metabolism 21.3 (2007): 445-461.</ref>，並令其腦部釋出使人感到愉快的化學物質（[[内啡肽|内啡肽]]），使人在心理上更為渴望這種刺激。人們亦可在觸摸性伴侶的性器官或其他身體部分的過程中感到性興奮。刺激龜頭和陰蒂會觸發{{link-en|球海綿體肌反射|bulbocavernosus reflex}}<ref name=Wheeless>http://www.wheelessonline.com/ortho/bulbocavernosus_reflex {{Wayback|url=http://www.wheelessonline.com/ortho/bulbocavernosus_reflex |date=20071213043458 }} Bulbocavernosus Reflex – Wheeless' Textbook of Orthopaedics</ref>。

[[性玩具|性玩具]]是指一些専門用於為受刺激者提供性刺激和愉快感的物件<ref name="Big book">{{cite book |last=Taormino |first=Tristan |title=The Big Book of Sex Toys |publisher=Quiver |year=2009 |isbn=978-1-59233-355-4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Hfly-iMkWRkC&pg=PP1 |page=30|access-date=2018-05-22 |archive-date=2016-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430062109/https://books.google.com/books?id=Hfly-iMkWRkC&pg=PP1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=sex toy|url=https://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/english-chinese-traditional/sex-toy|work=Cambridge Dictionary|accessdate=2021-03-09|publisher=Cambridge University Press|archive-date=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029212423/http://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/english-chinese-traditional/sex-toy|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|30}}。它們可為當事人自行使用，亦可在跟伴侶性事過程中加入之<ref name="Big book"/>{{rp|10}}。它們可提供人體不能提供之刺激<ref name="Big book"/>{{rp|29}}。

人類使用性玩具去進行性刺激的歷史已有千年之久。考古學家發現，[[旧石器时代|旧石器时代]]的人類已經會造出由矽石製成，兼經過打磨的[[假陰莖|假陰莖]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sci/tech/4713323.stm|title=Ancient Phallus Unearthed in Cave.|date=2005-07-25|accessdate=2021-03-11|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202125050/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sci/tech/4713323.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外古人亦會製作以骆驼粪和树脂為原料的假陰莖<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Book of Kink: Sex Beyond the Missionary|last=Christina, E.|publisher=Tarcher Perigree|year=2011|isbn=9781101545096|location=New York|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SFcWmcGLXJ4C|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819213328/https://books.google.com/books?id=SFcWmcGLXJ4C|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歷史學家尚不清楚它們有著怎樣的用途——它們可能是為[[仪式|宗教仪式]]而製造出來，亦可能是為了個人享樂而誕生。目前已知祈求多產的仪式當中會使用假陰莖<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.alternet.org/sex-amp-relationships/sex-toy|title=The long, strange history of sex toys.|date=2013-06-19|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2018-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181110080435/https://www.alternet.org/sex-amp-relationships/sex-toy|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。 不過[[古希腊|古希腊人]]會以皮革或动物肠道包著雕刻好的假陰莖，用以使其質感更自然<ref name=":1" />。 古羅馬人則製作了可供兩人使用的雙頭假陰莖。古代中國的假陰莖則由[[青铜|青铜]]等金屬製成，其中一些甚至可往內注入液體，以模擬男性的[[射精|射精]]<ref>{{Cite book|title=With the hand: a cultural history of masturbation|last=Driel, M.|publisher=Reaktion Books.|year=2012|isbn=9781861899576|location=London|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rPohFHqyrZ4C|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819210706/https://books.google.com/books?id=rPohFHqyrZ4C|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時中國上流社會的男性不少都納了妾，故此她們便在僧多粥少的情況下需用到假陰莖取樂。古波斯人視[[处女膜|处女膜]]的血為不潔之物，該些血液丈夫應避免接觸。故此在結婚的前一晚，當地的聖人會以由石頭製成的假陰莖把處女膜破掉，並藉此確認該名女性是否屬於處女之身<ref>{{Cite book|title=Marriage customs of the world: from henna to honeymoons|last=Monger, G.|publisher=ABC-Clio|year=2004|isbn=9781576079874|location=California|url=https://books.googl