=== 嗅觉 ===
嗅觉訊息對於人類性行為當中扮演重要角色。一项调查嗅觉性刺激的研究发现，男性會对女性香水產生性興奮。當中研究對象會對嗅觉刺激和感受到的性興奮進行評價。研究者亦在實驗期間透過[[功能性磁共振成像|功能性磁共振成像]]掃描對象的腦部。結果顯示女性香水的嗅覺刺激會使男性與性興奮相關的腦區活化<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Huh | first1 = J. | last2 = Park | first2 = K. | last3 = Hwang | first3 = I. S. | last4 = Jung | first4 = S. I. | last5 = Kim | first5 = H. J. | last6 = Chung | first6 = T. W. | last7 = Jeong | first7 = G. W. | year = 2008 | title = Brain activation areas of sexual arousal with olfactory stimulation in men: A preliminary study using functional MRI | url = http://www.jsm.jsexmed.org/article/S1743-6095(15)31972-X/fulltext | journal = The Journal of Sexual Medicine | volume = 5 | issue = 3 | pages = 619–625 | doi = 10.1111/j.1743-6109.2007.00717.x | pmid = 18221282 | access-date = 2021-03-12 | archive-date = 2020-05-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200527170155/https://www.jsm.jsexmed.org/article/S1743-6095(15)31972-X/fulltext | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

從演化的角度而言，人類繁殖策略上的性別差異有助於解釋氣味在性興奮當中的重要性——氣味与免疫学特征和後代的生存能力有关<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Rikowski | first1 = A. | last2 = Grammer | first2 = K. | year = 1999 | title = Human body odour, symmetry and attractiveness | journal = Proceedings of the Royal Society of London B: Biological Sciences | volume = 266 | issue = 1422| pages = 869–874 | doi=10.1098/rspb.1999.0717| pmid = 10380676 | pmc = 1689917 }}</ref>。嗅觉线索可能會觸發人們遺傳下來的[[近親性交|近親性交]]迥避機制。一項研究顯示，男性在選擇伴侶時會把視覺和嗅覺訊息放在同等位置看待，而女性則把嗅覺訊息視為最重要的變量。此外女性會把[[體味|體味]]視為眾多感官刺激當中，最對慾望構成負面影響的因素<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Herz | first1 = R. S. | last2 = Cahill | first2 = E. D. | year = 1997 | title = Differential use of sensory information in sexual behavior as a function of gender | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/225106584 | format = PDF | journal = Human Nature | volume = 8 | issue = 3| pages = 275–286 | doi=10.1007/bf02912495| pmid = 26196967 }}</ref>。

=== 聽覺 ===
聽覺刺激可能會強化性興奮度和快感。灵长类动物和人類常於性興奮和性行為期間從口中發出聲息——比如叹息、呻吟、深快的呼吸、在高潮时发出狂喜的尖叫声。對於兩性而言，該些聲息能使人高度興奮，為性反應創造正反饋<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Levin | first1 = R. J. | year = 1992 | title = The mechanisms of human female sexual arousal | journal = Annual Review of Sex Research | volume = 3 | pages = 1–48 | doi=10.1080/10532528.1992.10559874}}</ref>。[[叫床|叫床]]可能使交配者互相性刺激對方<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Hamilton | first1 = W. J. | last2 = Arrowood | first2 = P. C. | year = 1978 | title = Copulatory vocalizations of chacma baboons (Papio ursinus), gibbons (Hylobates hoolock), and humans | journal = Science | volume = 200 | issue = 4348| pages = 1405–1409 | doi=10.1126/science.663622 | pmid = 663622| bibcode = 1978Sci...200.1405H }}</ref>。

即使沒有觸覺上的配合，聲音本身就可以使人高度性興奮。商业色情材料（主要面向男性）廣泛採用令人興奮的声音。早在1920年代起，便有歌手藉著低吟來產生情色效果。[[歌舞杂耍表演|歌舞杂耍表演]]爵士歌手經常將性愛的聲音融入到歌词之中。像《性高潮》（由[[王子_(音樂家)|王子]]所創）和《{{link-en|你一定愛到球|You Sure Love to Ball}}》（由[[马文·盖伊|马文·盖伊]]所創）般的當代音樂加入了女性性高潮時所發出的聲息<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Corbett | first1 = J. | last2 = Kapsalis | first2 = T. | year = 1996 | title =  Aural Sex: The Female Orgasm in Popular Sound| journal =  TDR| volume = 40 | issue = 3| pages = 102–111 | doi=10.2307/1146553 }}</ref>。研究顯示，音樂可在聽覺上對人產生性刺激。一项情绪诱导研究發現，接触某些音乐可使男性的阴茎[[勃起|勃起]]和增强主观的性兴奋程度<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Mitchell | first1 = W. B. | last2 = DiBartolo | first2 = P. M. | last3 = Brown | first3 = T. A. | last4 = Barlow | first4 = D. H. | year = 1998 | title = Effects of positive and negative mood on sexual arousal in sexually functional males | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_1998-04_27_2/page/197 | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 27 | issue = 2| pages = 197–207 | doi = 10.1023/A:1018686631428 | pmid = 9562901 }}</ref>。另一項類似的研究則顯示，女性雖不會對某些類型的音樂產生生理反應，但仍報稱指的確提升了主觀性興奮程度<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Laan | first1 = E. | last2 = Everaerd | first2 = W. | last3 = Van Berlo | first3 = R. | last4 = Rijs | first4 = L. | year = 1995 | title = Mood and sexual arousal in women | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_behaviour-research-and-therapy_1995-05_33_4/page/441 | journal = Behaviour Research and Therapy | volume = 33 | issue = 4| pages = 441–443 | doi=10.1016/0005-7967(94)00059-s| pmid = 7755530 }}</ref>。之後亦有研究探討了聽覺刺激跟性快感體驗的關係。結果表明，儘管成為研究對象的男性對視覺刺激產生最高程度的生理和主觀性興奮，但他人的口語亦能使他們興奮——這意味着聲音的確可作為性刺激的手段<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Julien | first1 = E. | last2 = Over | first2 = R. | year = 1988 | title = Male sexual arousal across five modes of erotic stimulation | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_1988-04_17_2/page/131 | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 17 | issue = 2| pages = 131–143 | doi=10.1007/bf01542663| pmid = 2456050  }}</ref>。

== 心理刺激 ==
當人進入性興奮狀態時，其情感、慾望、吸引力、生理都會出現變化<ref name=":3">LeVay, S., & Valente, S. M. (2006). ''Human sexuality'' (2nd ed.). Sunderland, MA: Sinauer Associates.</ref>。这些不仅可以以身體上的刺激達至，像幻想、情色文学、梦境、角色扮演般的心理刺激同樣有着類近的效果。
